      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,15 @@\n+## \ud83d\ude80 Features\n+\n+### Initial release\n+\n+First release of the Security Lake Tools CLI with support for creating AWS Security Lake custom sources for OCSF event classes. Includes automatic IAM role creation, AWS account auto-detection, and SSO token expiration handling.\n+\n+*By @mavam.*\n+\n+## \ud83d\udd27 Changes\n+\n+### Remove Python 3.10 and 3.11 support\n+\n+The minimum Python version is now 3.12. The CI test matrix now covers Python 3.12 and 3.13.\n+\n+*By @mavam and @claude.*"
